title: Oak RIdge Boys 1967-1977 10 Years of Music
description: Oak Ridge Boys, (almost) complete recordings 1967-1977.  Includes their band's 1977 Swedish album, "Rockland Road, Planet Time" (only available in Europe) and the Oaks first country album "Live."  Sorry, does not include the 1973 recording, "Hymns."   Includes the very rare flipside single "Look Away Mama."  Almost impossible to find a hard copy.  Also a live copy of "Plant A Seed."  98% of this is analog off LPs.
